verbose_text: Before using photoacoustic imaging to detect the activity of MMPs in vivo, we first measure the PA signals of free BHQ3 (0.1 mg/ml), free CuS nanoparticles (0.8 mg/ml), and CPQ (0.8 mg/ml) before and after enzyme cleavage in solutions.
